{"tid":678357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18間航空公司已按北京要求修改台港澳標示","createTime":"2018-05-26T04:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T04:35:43.000Z","uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd396fcee5ca5ddfd237d6390250305d352e386","tid":678357,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】北京當局要求多間外國航空公司不得將台灣列為國家限期已經屆滿，大陸民航局說，已經有18間完成修改。<br />\n<br />\n民航局網站指，在上月底致函給44間外國航空公司，要求它們在30日內糾正官網相關內容中，違反大陸法律違背「一個中國」政策的錯誤做法。<br />\n<br />\n截至昨日，44間航空公司中有18間完成修改，其餘26間因為技術原因申請延期，並承諾整改，最遲會在7月25日完成。<br />\n<br />\n民航局表示，將密切關注這些航空公司的整改情況，並依法保障外國航空公司在華開展業務的權利。<br />\n<br />\n民航局上月底要求多間外國航空公司修改對台港澳的稱呼，不得將這些地方列為「國家」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=307132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307132&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=16e89672\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307132&h=a2b02394\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=307132</a>"},{"pid":"73c7e940d93d7fd6e03aa723f0f7317316bdd1b4","tid":678357,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"1984不遠矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f330e0c619fdb3dd6ff263a15a6f6cc46a9e2ed","tid":678357,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"幾時寄埋信要求外國將台港澳當成支國國民一樣待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187d33316850ce1fac63f0f788b5b9204cdf7682","tid":678357,"uid":60023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"改撚左淘寶送埋去香港先啦 大把連登仔支持"}]}